<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink86-kilavi">
      <p type="edition">putalvaṉ kūṟiya māṟṟam talaimakaṭkup pāṅkāyiṉār kūṟak kēṭṭāṉ eṉpatu āṟinta parattai ataṟkup pulantu talaimakaṟkuc colliyatu.
      </p>
      <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="Aink86">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>veṇṭalaik kurukiṉ meṉpaṟai viḷikkura</l>
<l>ṉīḷvaya ṉaṇṇi yimiḻu mūra</l>
<l>vemmiva ṇalkuta laritu</l>
<l>nummaṉai maṭantaiyoṭu talaippey tīmē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

<l>   O man from a village</l> 
<l rend="indent4"> 	that resounds with </l> 
<l rend="indent4"> 	the calling voices and soft wing[-beats] of white-headed herons </l> 
<l rend="indent4"> 	as they aproach the long fields! </l> 
<l> It is difficult for us to stay here.</l> 
<l> Please meet with the woman (i.e. your wife?) in your home! </l> 

  
  </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
